posts.title: At this point, I think it's obvious that we need more maga companies.
posts.content:
IDK wtf musk is talking about with all of his "talented" engineers. His cars are notoriously shit, and we could honestly have better internet if we simply told the regulators to fuck off.

Im sorry, but I think the whole giga press thing was fucking retarded from the get go. IDK what is so damn hard about making cars using body on frame construction using extruded C channel.

Electric motors can still be used in combination with a diesel generator. The generator can spin at a fixed rpm. By doing so, you can run it at it's efficiency peak and burn all the particulates without a stupid def system. Good old fashion Le Tourneau setup.

Since you have diesel onboard, you can make the motors AC induction motors or switched reluctance motors and get rid of the chinese commie magnets.

You can make the engine a giant 3L 2 cylinder boxer motor to save on cost, weight, and complexity. All it has to do is turn a generator, so who gives a fuck how many cylinders it has, so long as it's balanced.

And just for 1 final "fuck you" lets put in cloth seats from the 90s. They weren't blistering hot in the summer, and didn't freeze your nuts off in the winter.

Shazam. There is your american car. I bet you any fucking dumb shit american welder who can lay down some dimes could build something like that in a month.
